INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("84", "1", "2015-06-30 14:12:40", "2015-06-30 14:12:40", "<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<h3>History</h3>\r\nThis call comes as Waterwise launch 365 water saving tips, one for everyday of the year which everyone can get involved in. Metros Youth Chances Survey 2014 found that more than half of gay young people had experienced either discrimination or harassment. Two more major government departments - DWP and HMRC - are now going through the process to become foster-family-friendly employers. Thats why its so important that we continue to join up services such as health and housing and thats exactly what these projects will help to do. Natural England is very concerned to hear that a further male hen harrier has disappeared from Geltsdale in the north of England, resulting in its partner abandoning her nest.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\r\n<h3>Philosophy, Values, Missions</h3>\r\nThis call comes as Waterwise launch 365 water saving tips, one for everyday of the year which everyone can get involved in. Metros Youth Chances Survey 2014 found that more than half of gay young people had experienced either discrimination or harassment. Two more major government departments - DWP and HMRC - are now going through the process to become foster-family-friendly employers. Thats why its so important that we continue to join up services such as health and housing and thats exactly what these projects will help to do. Natural England is very concerned to hear that a further male hen harrier has disappeared from Geltsdale in the north of England, resulting in its partner abandoning her nest.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\r\n<h3>Community Involvement</h3>\r\nThis call comes as Waterwise launch 365 water saving tips, one for everyday of the year which everyone can get involved in. Metros Youth Chances Survey 2014 found that more than half of gay young people had experienced either discrimination or harassment. Two more major government departments - DWP and HMRC - are now going through the process to become foster-family-friendly employers. Thats why its so important that we continue to join up services such as health and housing and thats exactly what these projects will help to do. Natural England is very concerned to hear that a further male hen harrier has disappeared from Geltsdale in the north of England, resulting in its partner abandoning her nest.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\r\n<h3>Our Commitment to Quality</h3>\r\nThis call comes as Waterwise launch 365 water saving tips, one for everyday of the year which everyone can get involved in. Metros Youth Chances Survey 2014 found that more than half of gay young people had experienced either discrimination or harassment. Two more major government departments - DWP and HMRC - are now going through the process to become foster-family-friendly employers. Thats why its so important that we continue to join up services such as health and housing and thats exactly what these projects will help to do. Natural England is very concerned to hear that a further male hen harrier has disappeared from Geltsdale in the north of England, resulting in its partner abandoning her nest.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12\">\r\n<h3>Leadership</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4\"><img class=\"img-circle aligncenter\" src=\"http://mychoice.localhost/content/uploads/2015/06/mark-born-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Born\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n<h4>Linda Smith</h4>\r\nThis call comes as Waterwise launch 365 water saving tips, one for everyday of the year which everyone can get involved in. Metros Youth <img class=\"img-circle aligncenter\" src=\"http://mychoice.localhost/content/uploads/2015/06/mark-born-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Born\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n<h4>Linda Smith</h4>\r\nThis call comes as Waterwise launch 365 water saving tips, one for everyday of the year which everyone can get involved in. Metros Youth Chances Survey 2014 found that more than half of gay young people had experienced either discrimination or harassment. Two more major government departments - DWP and HMRC - are now going through the process to become foster-family-friendly employers.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4\"><img class=\"img-circle aligncenter\" src=\"http://mychoice.localhost/content/uploads/2015/06/mark-born-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Mark Born\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\n<h4>Linda Smith</h4>\r\nThis call comes as Waterwise launch 365 water saving tips, one for everyday of the year which everyone can get involved in. Metros Youth Chances Survey 2014 found that more than half of gay young people had experienced either discrimination or harassment. Two more major government departments - DWP and HMRC - are now going through the process to become foster-family-friendly employers.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\r\n<h3>Governing Meeting Board</h3>\r\nThis call comes as Waterwise launch 365 water saving tips, one for everyday of the year which everyone can get involved in. Metros Youth Chances Survey 2014 found that more than half of gay young people had experienced either discrimination or harassment. Two more major government departments - DWP and HMRC - are now going through the process to become foster-family-friendly employers. Thats why its so important that we continue to join up services such as health and housing and thats exactly what these projects will help to do. Natural England is very concerned to hear that a further male hen harrier has disappeared from Geltsdale in the north of England, resulting in its partner abandoning her nest.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\r\n<h3>Schedule</h3>\r\nInsert Schedule Here!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>", "About Us",